  "display_name": "Sustainable Finance and Green Bonds",
  "description": "This cluster of papers explores the impact of green bonds on climate finance, financial stability, and the transition to a low-carbon economy. It investigates the pricing of green bonds, their influence on corporate performance, and their role in financing sustainable development. The cluster also delves into the implications for monetary policy and the management of climate risks in the financial system.",
